            <did><unittitle>Series II: Chess</unittitle>
            </did>
            <scopecontent><p>The materials in this two-box series document Walter Goldwater's interest and
                  involvement in the game of chess. Some of the material related to Goldwater's
                  membership in the Marshall Chess Club. Other materials include records and
                  photographs of the Harlem Chess Tournament he helped to organize, and
                  correspondence from Book Shop customers interested in books on chess and other
                  board games.</p>
            </scopecontent>
